body_html: @freedomtan Apologies, I've only just noticed that you opened this PR on 17 January 2018, i.e. between TF 1.4 (2 November 2017) and TF 1.5 (26 January 2018), while I didn't have any problem building on aarch64 platforms until 1.8 (19 April 2018). So your fix has helped me to make progress on building TF 1.9, but the actual failure is different. Thanks.
